13 , 14 . ( a ) Ñanyi bintu byawama Yehoba byo akobila bashingwa ?
( b ) Ñanyi mwingilo bashingwa ye bakobila bantu ?
Yehoba ukamwesha byepi lusa lwanji lukatampe ku “ mikooko ikwabo ” kulutwe ?
Abano bonse bakebasangula pa kuba’mba bakatwajijile kwingijila Yehoba .
Yoano wanembele’mba : “ Namwene bantu bafwile bakatampe ne bacheche saka baimana kulutwe ya jitanda , kabiji mivungilo beivungulwile .
